<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>API Gateway Integrator — Ekosistem UMKM</title>
    <meta name="description" content="API Gateway / Integrator — Middleware pengendali ekosistem ekonomi UMKM. Kelompok 7 RPL 2 ULBI.">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/kong-theme.css">
    <style>
        .hero-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .hero-logo {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0033d4, #00a4ff);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 51, 212, 0.3);
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .feature-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .feature-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .btn-hero {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .btn-outline-light {
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            background: transparent;
        }
        .btn-outline-light:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="no-sidebar">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="hero-logo">IG</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Gateway Integrator</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Enterprise-grade API Gateway Middleware untuk Ekosistem Ekonomi UMKM.<br>
            Menangani Routing, Validasi JWT, Logging, dan Fee Management.
        </p>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Validasi JWT Otomatis</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Mencegah akses ilegal dengan verifikasi token berstandar industri sebelum diteruskan ke tujuan.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔀</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Dynamic API Routing</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Meneruskan request secara cerdas ke 6 layanan microservices dalam ekosistem UMKM.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Monetisasi Otomatis</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Pemotongan fee gateway 0.5% secara otomatis untuk setiap transaksi yang berhasil.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                <div class="feature-title">Audit Logging Real-time</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">Pencatatan menyeluruh untuk IP, waktu, metode, URL, dan response status.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary btn-hero">Buka Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/client-portal" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-hero">Client Portal (API Test)</a>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 32px;">
            <a href="/api/status" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: none;">📡 Cek Status API (Health Check)</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>